  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nIf a contact is renamed, the alias does not show in the mentions and it still shows the username instead.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. start a chat with a contact\r\n2. go to that contact profile, click nickname and rename the contact\r\n3. in the chat input try mentioning the contact\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nshould show the nickname in the mention list\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n(should show 'hello')\r\n\r\n![Screen Shot 2022-04-08 at 4 55 29 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/176720/162529018-d41c5881-bcfe-49d7-8731-31944b5a1225.png)\r\n\r\n",
